author: Slidebean
description:
A fully AI staffed startup shows what “one person companies” will really look like

Wired created a startup with 100% AI employees. Day one: fake reports, imaginary meetings, nonexistent offsites. After new rules and human oversight?

The AI team actually built a real product and investors liked it. The future isn’t “no employees.”
It’s you managing an army of bots.

👉Hear the full breakdown on The Slidebean Stand-Up; streaming now on Spotify, Apple Podcasts, and all major podcast platforms.
title: This all AI startup lied, cheated, hallucinated and still shipped a product.

author: Slidebean
description:
TikTok adds AI filters and screen time rewards but will it change behavior?

TikTok introduced new features allowing users to filter out AI content and earn badges for limiting screen time.

While the moves suggest a push toward digital well being, the limits remain fully skippable, raising questions about whether the goal is meaningful change or positive optics.

In a world built on engagement metrics, true reform may require more than optional reminders.

👉Hear the full breakdown on The Slidebean Stand-Up; streaming now on Spotify, Apple Podcasts, and all major podcast platforms.
title: TikTok wants you to scroll less, allegedly.
